		<p class="date">Sat Aug 10, 2013 at 01:00 PM PDT</p>
		<h2><a id="titleHref" href="/story/2013/08/10/1230134/-Green-diary-rescue-Chevron-protest-fracking-methane-in-Utah-Fukishima-leaks-into-ocean">Green diary rescue: Chevron protest, fracking methane in Utah, Fukushima leaks into ocean </a><span style="white-space: nowrap"></span></h2>
		
		<p class="author"><span>by</span> <a href="/user/Meteor Blades">Meteor Blades</a><a class="ajax type-user do-hotlist do-updateContent size-tiny off altTooltip" alt="Follow this author" href="#?friend_id=6&is_stream=1">Follow</a> <span class="for">for</span> <a href="/blog/main">Daily Kos</a></p>
    
    <ul class="front-page-share clearfix">
      
